_sText:
Features-
*Lots of secrets (none too imbalanced)
*More than 64 spawns
*Custom lightings
*HDR
*Cubemaps
*Large, perfect for huge populations
*Area Portals / Hints / Skips / Normal Compile Mode

Lots of interesting stuffs including:
-Chicken gun (on roof of ramp building)
-Colour changing room
-Zombie pusher machine (behind corner room)
-Funny face (press E on the wall on the left of 3 vending machine room)
-Secret "moon". Teleport is under a staircase.
-Secret speed gun. (Jump out of window of third floor of main building to teleport to entrance. Code is 3 numbers only)
-Iron curtain room. Get lots of people in that room and hold out the zombies by only using bullets
-Secret weapon room (under first floor of main building)

This map's various interesting stuffs was made by me (LightningZLaser) and desert theme made by ANBU.

*I do not know where the chicken model came from so if anyone knows pls give me the link to the model so I can give the credits.
